Description_lang:
Your successful Judgments $?s112859[generate a charge of Holy Power and ][]reduce the cast time and mana cost of your next Flash of Light$?s2812[, Divine Light, or Holy Radiance][] by $114250s1% per stack and improves its effectiveness by $114250s2% per stack when used to heal others. Stacks up to 3 times.

|CFFFFFFFFHoly|R
Judgments also generate a charge of Holy Power and Divine Light and Holy Radiance are also affected.

Fires a Divine Star in front of you, traveling 24 yds, causing $110745s1 Divine damage to all enemies and $110745s2 healing to all allies within 4 yds of its path.

After reaching its destination it will return to you, also dealing damage and healing to all targets in its path.

Deals Spellshadow damage and healing while in Shadowform.

Creates a ring of Holy energy around you that quickly expands and grows in power, up to 30 yds away. Deals up to ${$120692s2*0.1} to ${$120692S2} Holy damage to enemies, and up to ${$120692s1*0.1} to ${$120692S1} healing to allies, with the greatest effect at 25 yds.

Deals Shadow damage and healing while in Shadowform.
Grants an improved version of Shadowfiend that is substantially more effective at dealing damage and generating mana.

Protects the target with a shield of Holy Light for $d. The shield absorbs up to ${$m1+1.17*$SPH} damage every $t1 sec.

Can be active only on one target at a time.

|CFFFFFFFFHoly|R
Sacred Shield has no target limit, but a mana cost, and 3 charges with a 10 sec recharge time.
